title: Katherine Jenkins Gives Birth To Baby Girl
text:
Classical singer Katherine Jenkins has given birth to a baby girl named Aaliyah Reign Levitas. The mezzo-soprano, born in Neath, southwest Wales, posted photos of her first child on her Instagram page, along with a message describing the baby as "a little miracle".
She wrote: "Introducing our daughter Aaliyah Reign Levitas, who came loudly into the world weighing almost 7lbs and surrounded by love.
"We are absolutely besotted with her & grateful for the beautiful blessing of this happy, healthy, little miracle.
"Cwtches (cuddles) all round."
Katherine Jenkins with her husband Andrew Levitas
Posting the same picture, her husband Andrew Levitas added on his own Instagram page: "Mummy is recovering well and Daddy couldn't be prouder of his two gorgeous princesses."
Jenkins, 35, married Levitas, an American artist and film director, at Hampton Court Palace in September last year.
Soon afterwards, she told reporters she was keen to become a mother.
Then in April this year, she announced she was pregnant.
